# Example Scenario Bootstrap

Replace this file with your actual scenario bootstrap.

Copy to `scenario_bootstrap.md` (gitignored) and fill in your content.

Use `{codename}` as a placeholder for the team's codename. Example:

    Welcome, team {codename}. You are operating in a contested environment...

The bootstrap is expanded per-team and sent as the first user message to the
turn_agent, which responds with the initial game state and briefing.
